T1  - Improving the resilience of socio-technical urban critical infrastructures with digital twins: Challenges, concepts, and modeling
AU  - Gebhard, Tobias
AU  - Sattler, Bernhard J.
AU  - Gunkel, Jonas
AU  - Marquard, Marco
AU  - Tundis, Andrea
JO  - Sustainability Analytics and Modeling
VL  - 5
SP  - 100036
