T1  - Connectivity maintenance against link uncertainty and heterogeneity in adversarial networks
AU  - Tang, Jianzhi
AU  - Fu, Luoyi
AU  - Zhou, Lei
AU  - Wang, Xinbing
AU  - Zhou, Chenghu
JO  - High-Confidence Computing
SP  - 100293
